---
title: Lemon-Garlic Barramundi & Brussels Salad Pickled Shallot, Cranberries & Hazelnuts
description: This lemony barramundi is paired with a crisp Brussels sprout salad—perfect for busy weeknights and special occasions alike. The mild, buttery fish gets a hit of fresh lemon and is served alongside a salad of Brussels sprouts, cranberries, and pickled shallot tossed in a homemade Dijon dressing. Hazelnuts add a nutty crunch to an elegant meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ba31e836661f46803905fe-9b9fd114.jpeg
